name: Art Dox by JCODE x ASHU

metadata.name: Art Dox #1 - Bones
metadata.description:
"Art has its own flesh and bones,"

Art Dox by Jcode x Ashu" is project bringing generative art and poetry together. "Art Dox" an octave poem by Ashu was used as an input to create 8 unique generative art works by Jcode.
